{
  "stem": "7624.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a job, so to speak of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those people who were still alive, those who were in Spain or Russian and Polish and so on, came out from the underground, and we formed again the-- the organization.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, it was very difficult to find the children and to get them back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we had to find where are the parents of those children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them were gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were documentation, and some of them where it got lost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the difficult part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We asked people who had hidden children to come forward and tell us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a lot of the children, we never know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they kept the children there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In France, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know the others, which we never knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So with those children, we opened up again new children homes, and we put them in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we start to try to find out what happened to the family and the parents and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war, Drancy was a distribution center.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We found all the papers from every single person who was deported from France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those Germans had-- exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about over 70,000, or almost 80,000 people deported from France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know exactly when my parents and sister were deported, which transport, the number-- the name of the transport, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it says only 'direction Auschwitz.' That's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and that was after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the [INAUDIBLE], [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Klarsfeld, ?] she made a book, and she found out how many people came back from this transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she has a book of that, which I have, too, here.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
